::DarkMouse::
She felt his arm around her waist.  She stopped and stood still were she 
was.  She was afraid.  She didn't know what to do about this.  This was her 
commander.  Not only her superior, but a bot whom she was caring for a great 
deal.  She started to shake a little.
"Uh, all the help I can get commander."
She was blushing and couldn't stop. She just wasn't programmed for anything 
lke this. She never felt like this before and was just confused on what to 
do.
She turned and looked into his eyes.
"I like you a great deal commander."
All of a sudden she couldn't breath.  Her resporator didn't want to 
function. She felt light headed and the room started to spin.  She fainted 
and fell forward into Scorponok's arms.
